  "3142140": {
    "name": "Old Timer Transport",
    "steam_appid": 3142140,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >代步车、混乱和欢笑--欢迎来到你人生中最狂野的旅程！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/88859c930ac0acb36c2e0555f221f62d.poster.avif?t=1746385063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/88859c930ac0acb36c2e0555f221f62d.webm?t=1746385063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/88859c930ac0acb36c2e0555f221f62d.mp4?t=1746385063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>准备好在滑板车上大干一场了吗？</strong> 扮演一位脾气暴躁的老司机，驾驶一辆涡轮增压代步车，在邦皮多姆市中飞驰。你的任务是什么？捡起散落在各处的人类，并将他们送到安全地点，同时还要避开同样脾气暴躁的对手。PvP？当然。布娃娃物理？当然。笑声？保证。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/9e18d5e36515397096bc54e90a26933d.poster.avif?t=1746385063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/9e18d5e36515397096bc54e90a26933d.webm?t=1746385063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/9e18d5e36515397096bc54e90a26933d.mp4?t=1746385063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>这是你和其他人的较量！</strong> 无论你是用适时的爆炸将对手炸出赛道，还是飞速冲向医院，你和胜利之间的唯一阻隔就是这座充满混乱的城市。谁将成为最终的暴躁冠军？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/5defd5f159c6bb3bca7d064c059e7807.poster.avif?t=1746385063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/5defd5f159c6bb3bca7d064c059e7807.webm?t=1746385063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/5defd5f159c6bb3bca7d064c059e7807.mp4?t=1746385063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>期待意外</strong>，因为在这个游戏中，任何事情都可能（也必将）发生。从滑板车失控到行人被滑稽地扔到地图上，这一切都是乐趣的一部分。拥抱不可预知性，随波逐流（或崩溃)。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/f7a8e50b22b41caaf07e2039b5fbe95a.poster.avif?t=1746385063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/f7a8e50b22b41caaf07e2039b5fbe95a.webm?t=1746385063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/f7a8e50b22b41caaf07e2039b5fbe95a.mp4?t=1746385063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>有什么比独自制造混乱更好？<strong>当然是和朋友们一起制造混乱!</strong> 与好友一起玩耍，或树立新的敌人--因为没有什么比把他们从滑板车上扔下来更搞笑的事了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/a915d1e2e6a5b38162c29b205ef35afe.poster.avif?t=1746385063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/a915d1e2e6a5b38162c29b205ef35afe.webm?t=1746385063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142140/extras/a915d1e2e6a5b38162c29b205ef35afe.mp4?t=1746385063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你认为自己有能力成为终极暴躁司机吗？<strong>带上你的摩托车，召集你的朋友，一头扎进你人生中最荒唐的游戏中。</strong>城市在等着你--只要别撞车（撞得太猛）。🚀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > “系好安全带，这将是一次狂野之旅！”</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>准备好欢笑、愤怒，以及介于两者之间的一切。加入疯狂的行列，记住：滑板车不只是用来代步的，更是用来称霸的。🏆</strong></p>",
